description: The Taste of Eastern Europe is a truck roaming the streets of Washington, DC. As the name suggests, this truck offers traditional fare that reflects the Eastern European food culture. Dishes include a house made Tzatziki sauce, Kufte,  a very popular Bulgarian grilled item, bean salad with a chunky relish called Lutenica, and their own European spin on burgers and sandwiches.
name: The Taste Of Eastern Europe
